TitMainTitle: Group portrait of twelve men, including one second from left wearing dark jacket with crest inscribed "Phalanx", and eight women, posed behind small table with display of miniature flags, and bell, in Centre Avenue YMCA with sign in background reading "Atlas Spaceship, navigator John Douglas, pilots Wm. Albea and Lou Davenport...Titan Spaceship, navigator Lorraine McCoad, pilot Sara Robinson..."
